---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'May 18, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — SundayRec"
  description="Privacy Policy for SundayRec software and sundayrec.com"
>
  <header class="bg-[#194280] py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <img src="/images/sundayrec_primary_gull-paa-blaa.svg" alt="SundayRec" class="w-10 h-10" />
        <span class="font-bold text-lg text-white">SundayRec</span>
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-300 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-gray prose-headings:text-[#194280] prose-a:text-[#194280] max-w-none">

      <p>This Privacy Policy explains how Richard Fossland ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and protects information when you use SundayRec software and the sundayrec.com website ("Service").</p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>a) Information you provide directly</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email address:</strong> When you sign up for the Pro waitlist or contact us, we collect your email address.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment information:</strong> When you purchase a Pro subscription, payment is handled by Paddle. We do not store your credit card details — these are processed and stored securely by Paddle.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>b) Information collected automatically</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Website analytics:</strong> We may collect basic, anonymised usage data about visits to sundayrec.com (pages visited, browser type, country). No personally identifiable information is stored in analytics.</li>
        <li><strong>Auto-update checks:</strong> The SundayRec desktop app periodically checks for updates. This involves a network request to our update server that may include your app version and operating system. No personal data is transmitted.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>c) Information we do NOT collect</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>We do not access, upload, or store your audio recordings.</li>
        <li>We do not track your recording activity or schedules.</li>
        <li>All recordings remain on your local device at all times.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Send you product updates and announcements (only if you signed up for the waitlist)</li>
        <li>Process payments and manage your subscription</li>
        <li>Respond to support enquiries</li>
        <li>Improve the Service</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will never sell your personal data to third parties.</p>

      <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services that may process your data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Paddle</strong> — payment processing and subscription management. See <a href="https://www.paddle.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Paddle's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Formspree</strong> — email form submissions from the website. See <a href="https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Formspree's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>GitHub</strong> — hosts the application download files. See <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your email address for as long as you remain subscribed to our mailing list. You may unsubscribe at any time via the link in any email we send. Payment records are retained as required by law.</p>

      <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@sundayrec.com">hello@sundayrec.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>6. Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>The Service is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions or concerns about this policy? Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@sundayrec.com">hello@sundayrec.com</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-[#0f2a54] py-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm text-blue-300">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">← Back to home</a>
      <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Terms of Service</a>
      <a href="/refund" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Refund Policy</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
